components.name: Piston Rod
components.function: Transmits the suspension motion to the shock absorber piston

components.name: Shock Piston
components.function: Controls the movement and damping of the shock absorber

components.name: Damper Tube
components.function: Houses the shock absorber fluid, allowing controlled compression and extension

components.name: Mounting Bracket
components.function: Secures the shock absorber to the vehicle chassis or suspension components
